I always have trouble
saying that.

00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:23.880
So we're going to focus, really,
on cloud storage,

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:26.610
BigQuery, App Engine, and we're
going to talk a little

00:05:26.610 --> 00:05:28.160
bit about the prediction
API as well, and how

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:30.810
we plan to use that.

