00:05:37.330 --> 00:05:39.370
Why not build a cool
infrastructure?

00:05:39.370 --> 00:05:43.480
Why not have big data
projects internally?

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:47.460
And I sort of say, we do, but we
use Google because we like

00:05:47.460 --> 00:05:51.300
to focus on building products,
and trying to get away from

00:05:51.300 --> 00:05:52.100
building infrastructures.

00:05:52.100 --> 00:05:54.370
So really spending our time on
trying to make really, really,

00:05:54.370 --> 00:05:58.220
really fantastic games and
products for our customers.

00:05:58.220 --> 00:06:01.020
