And we can combine those.

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:02.900
Again, we can take them back
home, we can craft them into

00:10:02.900 --> 00:10:05.370
bigger and better items, and we
can carry on with the game.

00:10:05.370 --> 00:10:07.280
And the way that we lead players
through the game is

00:10:07.280 --> 00:10:08.640
really through the
questing system.

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.680
So players travel around the
world, and they meet

00:10:10.680 --> 00:10:12.690
non-player characters.

00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:14.320
And when they meet those
non-player characters, they're

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:16.180
given all sorts of different
tasks that they need to do.

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:18.390
So they start off very, very
simple, and then they progress

00:10:18.390 --> 00:10:20.600
and get more and more complex,
meaning that you really need

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:23.500
to get out there into the world,
find all these items,

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:27.080
discover them, and discover the
recipes on how you make

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:29.910
better and better items.

